# Python Project Configuration

## Requirement

All Python projects SHALL use `pyproject.toml` for project configuration and metadata.

Python projects SHALL NOT use `setup.py` for project configuration.

The `pyproject.toml` file SHALL contain all project metadata, dependencies, build system configuration, and tool configurations (e.g., mypy, ruff, pytest).

